	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think it's similar to (or even a much stronger version of) the phenomenon where people often find it uncomfortable or strange to listen to a recording of themselves speaking. <br /><br />The Jodi Sweetin quote sounds much less like being &quot;locked out&quot; of anything and more like a general disinterest in watching television. (She mentions having Netflix, and Full House is available on Netflix.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
